Some icons from both versions of Patalliro (the old and the new). Not many icons because I couldn't find almost any picture...
They were done for a contest, but I didn't win.

I have uploaded a couple of things at megaupload.com to share it at some forums, since it's there I may share it here as well:

***Loveless Ost: http://www.megaupload.com/?d=22ARERPW
Is really good, one of the ost I have liked most from what I have seen lately. The anime is very good too, if you have not see it yet, you should donwload it. You can get it via bittorrent here: http://animesuki.com/series.php/590.html

***PV: Scissor Sisters - Filthy/Gorgeous: http://www.megaupload.com/?d=06289CK9
A very interesting videoclip from that american band. I love the atmosphere of the vid.

Comment when you donwload and tell what you think of them.
